\n辯護人<br />\n共謀者<br />\n<br />\n不能盡錄..... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就算唔係邪勝正<br />\n仲有好多係同歸於盡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n韓國電影正義勝率係好低 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06eccc25200e29ce2d91a5a6481ffba63348fd17","tid":259010,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T09:28:13.000Z","msg":"其實漫畫都係意識形態既一種<br />\n所以夜神月果種觀念唔比佢主張<br />\n都係傳統既做法<br />\n<br />\n利伸：<br />\n我buy阿月果套 <br />\n呢個世界太多道德撚"},{"pid":"148f5c08b443a02dc1d224394c045e8d4f066dfd","tid":259010,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T09:28:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>可能道德觀問題<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你留意下香港電影<br />\n一樣係唔可以邪勝正</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過韓國電影<br />\n十套九套邪勝正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nrly?</blockquote><br />\n無間道1<br />\n恐怖雞<br />\n見鬼10<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n維多利亞一號<br />\n第一類型危險<br />\n轟天龍虎會<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12713fce4abc67082758af66fb3c80e956c2884b","tid":259010,"uid":115407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T09:31:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>應該都係關JUMP編輯部事<br />\n套套熱門作都要死唔斷命咁</blockquote><br />\n好在暗殺冇步佢後塵</blockquote><br />\n暗殺個故都好完整，最後仲要咁慛淚，近年佳作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc14528b4f1c517c6131d9ec4312fc8eb367e43b","tid":259010,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T09:33:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>可能道德觀問題<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你留意下香港電影<br />\n一樣係唔可以邪勝正</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\"